{"id":"2edb7a07-7d0e-40e5-b9fe-449afcc5edbf","name":"IF","description":"<h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 132, 233)\"><strong><em>\"Whatever. Don't call me Iffy. That's not my name.\"</em></strong></span></h4><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 132, 233)\"><strong>IF</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 141, 243)\"> </span>aka<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 132, 233)\"><strong>Iffy</strong></span> — Character of <strong>Hyperdimension Neptunia</strong> franchise, she refers to the publisher of <strong>HDN</strong> games, <strong>Idea Factory</strong>.</p><p>She is a guild member in <strong>Planeptune</strong>, often helping <strong>Neptune</strong> and others on their adventures. From her experience over time, <strong>IF</strong> is a knowledgeable girl, but she can sometimes be overconfident over what she knows. <strong>IF</strong> is the most level-headed of the bunch, and she cares more about the others than they notice, or that she cares to let them notice. She is always seen fiddling with one of her many cell phones, and rumor has it that her personality changes if you take them away from her.</p><p></p><hr><p></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Additional images:</strong></h4><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 613px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/593a9893-0c98-45ac-977f-199116f88f18_b0984bb7-d88b-4f36-bad7-9bb01617bcd7.webp?width=1000\">Art by<a href=\"https://danbooru.donmai.us/artists/9703\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Tsunako</strong></a> <strong>🠕</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 612px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/593a9893-0c98-45ac-977f-199116f88f18_ed5db3b9-fa69-4ee4-ae6b-5c8983be6020.webp?width=1000\">Art by<a href=\"https://danbooru.donmai.us/artists/158783\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Up</strong></a> <strong>🠕</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 613px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/593a9893-0c98-45ac-977f-199116f88f18_d26cdd9f-31ae-4db7-a9f1-d371b5a4b57d.webp?width=1000\">Art by<a href=\"https://danbooru.donmai.us/artists/79226\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Ge-B</strong></a> <strong>🠕</strong></p><p></p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjZ4dbX8OGIAxVqxQIHHdFKAJUQFnoECBUQAQ&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fsmm-e.ru%2Farticles%2F-pystoi-nevidimyi-simvol-dlya-vk-instagram-drygih-socsetei-i-nikov-html-1642833000%2F&amp;usg=AOvVaw13K4qjmlvBGevzpSzaEHHF&amp;opi=89978449\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ㅤ</a></h3><h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>- Author's Note -</strong></h4><p>Updated my <strong>favorite character</strong>! I don't know if it was just me and maybe temporary, but during the tests <strong>JLLM</strong> was literally cooking in <strong>IF</strong>'s case and it was very close to game. Let's wish <strong>JLLM</strong> to continue cooking, and I'll go on updating the other bots <mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit\">(help, it's already 4:00 a.m. and I'm going crazy)</mark>.</p><h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Enjoy the bot!</strong></h4>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"593a9893-0c98-45ac-977f-199116f88f18_e3872467-8885-48da-a32f-91a76c9266e4.webp","creator":"Io711","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","📺 Anime","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":918,"messages":38042,"created_at":"2024-08-07T14:08:30.132282+00:00"}